Name: ValiVictorian
About the game: ValiVictorian is a first-person horror mystery game that explores the world between our world and where spirits reside, following the story within a house that was once owned by a mad scientist. The abominations and puzzles that wait for the player inside might just shed some light on what is happening and how to stop it.
